				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="hatnote">This article is about the opera.  For the explorer, see <a href="/wiki/Christopher_Columbus" title="Christopher Columbus">Christopher Columbus</a>.</div>
