<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Synopsis">Synopsis</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Christophe_Colomb&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: Synopsis">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<p>The opera tells the life of Christopher Columbus in a series of episodes which avoid chronological order and are sometimes <a href="/wiki/Allegory" title="Allegory">allegorical</a>.</p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Sources">Sources</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Christophe_Colomb&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3" title="Edit section: Sources">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul>
<li><i>The Viking Opera Guide</i> ed. Holden (Viking, 1993)</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.delteatro.it/dizionario_dell_opera/c/christophe_colomb.php">Del Teatro (in Italian)</a></li>
